# the apt update, upgrade, dist upgrade, and autoremove features.              #
#                                                                              #
# Change History                                                               #
# 12/19/2019  Thomas Shuster: Original code. This is a script, intended for    #
#                           to be used to update the system.                   #
#                           Add new history entries as needed.                 #
#                                                                              #
#                                                                              #
